query: select q.id, choiceid, a.respondentid, a.surveyid,a.context, label, a.type,  (q.minresponses - q.maxresponses ) as response from questions q join answers a on q.id = a.questionid and q.surveyid = a.surveyid LEFT JOIN answersets a2 on a.surveyid = a2.surveyid and a.respondentid = a2.respondentid and a.context = a2.context and a.etl_time=a2.etl_time where a.surveyid = 8399 ;
